Clarence OCHS et al., Appellants, v. O. T. GILBANK et al., Appellees. No. 8665. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Dec. 2, 1937. John W. Carrigan, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellants. Raphael Dechter, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellees.

Before DENMAN, STEPHENS, and HEALY, • Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for the respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed, that a decree of dismissal be filed and entered accordingly, and that the mandate of this court issue forthwith.
